    "title": "Mid-Level Investment Banker at MCX International Enterprises",
    "description": "We at MCX International Enterprises are looking for an experienced Investment Banker based out of Vijayawada. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout MCX International Enterprises:\nMCX International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MCX International Enterprises!",
